# Coding standards

Applies to this repository.

- Follow **Prettier** (don’t fight it).
- Use **single quotes** in JS/TS/Vue.
- Group **type imports first**, then value imports; keep 1 blank line between groups.
- Prefer Nuxt alias **`~/`** for app code imports.
- Prefer shadcn wrappers (`components/ui/*`) + `cn()` for class composition.
- Prefer Tailwind named utilities when equivalent exists (avoid arbitrary values unless needed).

